# Invenio with elasticsearch support

## Requirements

- Elasticsearch 0.99.xx
- pip instal pyelasticsearch

## Installation
- downlaod from the source uncompress and add elaticsearch binary in your PATH var
- use the default config file located in invenio/ext/elasticsearch/config/elasticsearch.yml

## Developpment
- simply run: foreman start
- test:  python invenio/ext/elasticsearch/scripts/test_es.py
